snippet.textDisplay:
real story of Sohni and Mahiwal 
two lovers of Punjab near famous river "chanab" in pakistan present day.
and this is the folk song about them. 

The real story of two lovers, who never met and died during crossing of the river "chanab" because "sohni" always used to cross the river "Chanab" with the help of a Clay pot which is being used as an instrument in this song too here! but that day it was a bad weather plus "sohn's" relative keeps a wrong clay pot so that she drowns and dies and she did not know because she was running away from the enemies towards the other side of the river name "chanab" which is now in pakistan. she always used to cross it with the clay pot to meet her beloved "Mahiwal" but that day they both drowned and died because her beloved "mahiwal" jumped into the river to help her but they died as true lovers and became legends and history ! 

sad!
